沿革內容:
1. Enacted by the twenty-second Control Yuan plenary meeting on July 20, 1948;
2. Article 2 amended and promulgated on November 18, 1955, Ref: Chien-Tai-Yuan-Yi Tze No.2286;
3. The title was changed from ‘Regulations for Receiving People’s Written Complaints by the Control Yuan and its Members’ into the current one. Most articles were amended and promulgated on May 29, 1973, Ref: Chien-Tai-Yuan-Yi Tze No.1543;
4. Articles 3, 15, 17 amended and promulgated on June 20, 1975, Ref: Chien-Tai-Yuan-Yi Tze No.1428;
5. Article 3 amended and promulgated on June 8, 1984, Ref: Chien-Tai-Yuan-Yi Tze No.1533;
6. Article 6 amended and promulgated on September 14, 1984, Ref: Chien-Tai-Yuan-Yi Tze No.2430;
7. The amendment of all 15 articles was promulgated on October 30, 1993, Ref: Yuan-Tai-San-Chia Tze No.6357;
8. The amendment of articles was promulgated on November 14, 1995 by the thirty-fifth plenary meeting of the second term of the Control Yuan;
9. Article 6, 8, 9, 10 amended on March 24, 1998 by the seventy-eighth plenary meeting of the second term of the Control Yuan;
